1
00:00:08,997 --> 00:00:12,524
Muraho, ikaze kuri icyi cyiciro
ku isesengura ry' amahirwe yo kubona isoko.

2
00:00:12,524 --> 00:00:14,665
Mu by'ukuri byitwa kureba mbere y'uko ubiba

3
00:00:14,665 --> 00:00:17,458
Byitwa bityo kuko
ibyo ari byo byakabaye bikorwa.

4
00:00:17,458 --> 00:00:19,587
Reba mbere yo kubiba
mu gice cy'amasoko.

5
00:00:19,934 --> 00:00:23,430
Ibyo yabonye inshuro nyinshi
ni uko ba rwiyemezamirimo b'abatangizi

6
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:26,736
Binjira mu gice cya mbere cy'isoko
bafata,

7
00:00:26,736 --> 00:00:29,673
ariko uru si uruhererekane
twagiramo inama abantu,

8
00:00:29,673 --> 00:00:31,864
Kubera ibisubizo
biba aho

9
00:00:31,864 --> 00:00:34,959
bikubwira ko wakabanje ukareba
 ku mahirwe anyuranye

10
00:00:35,536 --> 00:00:38,545
hanyuma ugahitamo ayo
ugiye gukoresha.

11
00:00:38,780 --> 00:00:43,219
Kubakira kuri iyo ngingo
ni igice dushaka kumva

12
00:00:43,219 --> 00:00:45,583
Icyo gice kikaba ari amahirwe meza cyane.

13
00:00:46,434 --> 00:00:48,368
Akaba ari amahirwe aguha

14
00:00:48,368 --> 00:00:51,621
Ubutaka bwera kurusha ubundi
mu gihe uri kurema ibikorwa.

15
00:00:51,621 --> 00:00:53,784
Nk'iko mubyibuka,
amahirwe yose ntasa,

16
00:00:53,784 --> 00:00:59,148
Dukeneye kumva ibice 
bikurura by'amahirwe.

17
00:00:59,148 --> 00:01:03,540
N'ibice byagufasha 
kurema ibikorwa bizaramba

18
00:01:03,832 --> 00:01:07,862
Mu gice gishize twavuze
ku mahitamo y'imikurire.

19
00:01:07,862 --> 00:01:10,963
Ibyo nibyo 
iyi foto iri aha yerekana,

20
00:01:10,963 --> 00:01:13,403
kandi nk'uko mubyibuka,
twari dufite amahirwe menshi anyuranye

21
00:01:13,403 --> 00:01:15,328
afatiye ku ikoranabuhanga ryawe.

22
00:01:15,328 --> 00:01:18,435
Ikibazo kiza, ni ayahe muri ayo  mahirwe y'amasoko

23
00:01:18,435 --> 00:01:22,297
ari meza kuyinjiramo,
ku muryango/ kampani yanyu?

24
00:01:23,995 --> 00:01:27,819
Iki kibazo ushobora kugicamo 
ibibazo bibiri by'ingenzi

25
00:01:27,819 --> 00:01:31,382
ndetse n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi
tuza kujyaho impaka nyuma,

26
00:01:31,382 --> 00:01:36,066
ariko risansi, ishya vuba
mu rwego rw'ubukungu.

27
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:39,466
Ese ni ikihe gice cy'isoko kiguha
ubutaka bwera kurusha ibindi

28
00:01:39,466 --> 00:01:41,271
ku bikorwa ushaka kurema?

29
00:01:41,271 --> 00:01:46,757
Bisobanura ko hari amasoko amwe n'amwe afite rukuruzi
 kurusha andi ku buryo umuntu yayinjiramo.

30
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:51,516
Icya kabiri, bihita bihinduka ikindi kibazo
kiri cyane cyane ku rweho rw'uburyo ibintu bishyirwa kuri gahunda.

31
00:01:51,516 --> 00:01:54,928
Isoko uiye kwinjiramo
riha inyito ibikorwa by'umuryango wawe,

32
00:01:54,928 --> 00:01:57,227
uwo uri we nk'umuryango.

33
00:01:57,227 --> 00:01:59,928
Bitewe n'isoko winjiyemo.

34
00:01:59,928 --> 00:02:03,721
ibi byaza nyuma biciye mu mucyo binyuranye.

35
00:02:03,721 --> 00:02:06,154
Icya gatatu, kandi tutagiyeho 
impaka cyane

36
00:02:06,154 --> 00:02:10,978
hari ibice bimwe ba bimwe wakumva
ubikunze kurusha ibindi.

37
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:15,982
Ibyo ukunda rero nibyo bigutwara 
bikomeye mu kwiyemeza imirimo.

38
00:02:15,982 --> 00:02:20,033
kuko byerekana aho ingufu,
kandi n'ibyo witaho cyane kurusha ibindi

39
00:02:20,033 --> 00:02:23,051
urebye ibibazo
wishimiye gukemura.

40
00:02:23,051 --> 00:02:26,230
nti mwakabaye mwibagirwa
ibijyanye n'igice cya gatatu,

41
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:29,027
kandi bishoboka ko waba witeguye
kujya miri ibyo bice

42
00:02:29,027 --> 00:02:31,340
Aho uvuga " mfitiye ubushobozi bwinshi"

43
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:34,326
mu gihe ibyo bice bitanga ubutaka bwera,

44
00:02:34,326 --> 00:02:36,476
ni byiza cyane.

45
00:02:36,476 --> 00:02:38,621
ariko hashobora kuba hariho isano ku byacurujwe.

46
00:02:38,621 --> 00:02:41,449
aho ibice byinsh
i bidatanga ubutaka bwera.

47
00:02:42,509 --> 00:02:45,146
igice wishimiye kandi ushobora
cyakabaye kiguha

48
00:02:45,146 --> 00:02:49,452
ibicuruzwa byinshi wacuruza

49
00:02:49,452 --> 00:02:52,988
byagufasha gukora kampani 
nshya kandi igakora neza.

50
00:02:54,268 --> 00:02:55,975
Iyo bibaye ikibazo cy'isano ry'ibyacurujwe,

51
00:02:55,975 --> 00:02:58,445
Iki ni ikibazo cy'ingenzi tutakwirengagiza,

52
00:02:58,445 --> 00:03:01,245
kuko wakabaye uniga 
gukunda ibice bimwe neza,

53
00:03:01,245 --> 00:03:05,192
igihe watangiye kubona bigenda 
neza muri icyo gice cyawe,

54
00:03:05,192 --> 00:03:07,890
ushobora kuvuga uti, " Ni byiza, iki 
ni igice cyiza cyo kubamo,"

55
00:03:07,890 --> 00:03:11,077
noneho ugatangira kumva 
ucyiyumvamo

56
00:03:11,077 --> 00:03:13,629
yego, ni gake gake
nko kubikunda iyo ukibibona bwa mbere,

57
00:03:13,629 --> 00:03:15,349
bwa kabiri,
ndetse n'ubwa gatatu.

58
00:03:16,369 --> 00:03:18,368
Tekereza kuri ibyo hanyuma turaza kureba

59
00:03:18,368 --> 00:03:21,266
ku bibazo birambuye
byagufasha kumva

60
00:03:21,266 --> 00:03:23,486
uko wasuzuma
amahirwe yawe y'amasoko 

61
00:03:24,184 --> 00:03:26,179
mu rwego rwo kumva
niba amahirwe yawe

62
00:03:26,179 --> 00:03:31,225
aguha ubutaka bwera
bugufasha kurera ibikorwa byawe bigakura,

63
00:03:31,225 --> 00:03:34,913
hari ibibazo
wakabaye wibaza

64
00:03:34,913 --> 00:03:37,455
byibaze kandi bitekereze ho,

65
00:03:37,455 --> 00:03:39,994
kandi twabishyse ku rutonde uri uru ruhande.

66
00:03:41,374 --> 00:03:44,424
Ibyo bibazo 
nyine bifitanye isano

67
00:03:44,424 --> 00:03:48,634
ariko bigufasha kugenda 
ubitekerezaho kimwe ku kindi.

68
00:03:48,634 --> 00:03:53,220
kuko buri kimwe muri ibyo bibazo
kireba ikibazo gikomeye.

69
00:03:53,225 --> 00:03:56,087
Twashatse ikinyuranyo hagati y'uko abakiriya babona ibintu,

70
00:03:56,087 --> 00:03:58,848
uko bigaragara ku isoko
n'uko bigaragara mu bukungu,

71
00:03:58,848 --> 00:04:01,899
uko bigaragara mu kubikorwa
n'uko bigaragara mu gihe ibikorwa biri gukura.

72
00:04:02,312 --> 00:04:04,757
Icya mbere ni uko abakiriya babibona.

73
00:04:04,757 --> 00:04:07,361
Uko abakiriya babibona 
bikwiye gutekerezwaho cyane.

74
00:04:07,361 --> 00:04:12,050
Nk'uko Peter Drucker yabivuze, ntabwo 
ukora kampani kugirango ukore ibicuruzwa,

75
00:04:12,050 --> 00:04:15,192
ukora kampani kugirango ureme amasoko mashya

76
00:04:15,192 --> 00:04:19,379
umukiriya niwe biheraho kugirango 
ureme isoko.

77
00:04:19,379 --> 00:04:23,241
ikibazo cy'ingenzi ni 
niba umukiriya ababara

78
00:04:23,241 --> 00:04:24,981
kuberako adafite ibicuruzwa byawe.

79
00:04:26,485 --> 00:04:29,323
Ugushaka ibicuruzwa byawe bifite izihe ngufu?

80
00:04:29,323 --> 00:04:32,286
Hari ibicuruzwa umukiriya avuga,
" Nshobora kugira iki,"

81
00:04:32,286 --> 00:04:34,722
hakaba n'ibindi bicuruzwa aho umukiriya avuga,
" Nakabaye mfite iki"

82
00:04:35,326 --> 00:04:38,674
Hakaba n'ibindi bicuruzwa avuga,
" Ngomba kugira iki"

83
00:04:40,613 --> 00:04:44,202
Biragaragara neza ko
ufite ibyo bagomba kuba bafite

84
00:04:44,202 --> 00:04:45,833
akaba ari byo uzanira abakiriya

85
00:04:45,833 --> 00:04:47,810
ku buryo bizaba
igicuruzwa kigurishwa byoroshye.

86
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:52,336
ikindi kintu ni uko 
wakabaye igerageza kongera inyungu.

87
00:04:53,076 --> 00:04:55,770
abakiriya bakura mu bicuruzwa byawe.

88
00:04:56,333 --> 00:04:59,893
ibi bikunda gukorwa byoroshye
mu buryo ubucuruzi bukorwa,

89
00:04:59,893 --> 00:05:03,644
aho wowe nk'urugero,
waba ufite igisubizo cyiza,

90
00:05:03,644 --> 00:05:07,744
ariko ibi byanakorwa
ku bw'isano ubucuruzi buba bufitanye  n'abakiriya

91
00:05:07,744 --> 00:05:09,130
aho ugerageza kumva

92
00:05:09,130 --> 00:05:12,150
ese ni inyungu yihe abakiriya 
babona mu bicuruzwa byawe

93
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:13,702
nk'urugero, niba ukoze porogaramu

94
00:05:13,702 --> 00:05:21,156
ishobora kuba ifasha abakiriya
kubona amakuru kandi nti banate n'umwanya.

95
00:05:21,158 --> 00:05:22,921
ako niko gaciro kagaragara.

96
00:05:22,921 --> 00:05:27,227
Cyangwa, ikamuhuza n'andi moko 
y'amakuru atashoboraga kubona.

97
00:05:27,227 --> 00:05:28,768
ako ni agaciro kagaragara.

98
00:05:30,298 --> 00:05:32,754
bihinduka ikibazo,
ufite umukiriya

99
00:05:32,754 --> 00:05:36,290
ushaka bikomeye
ibicuruzwa ucuruza?

100
00:05:36,290 --> 00:05:40,755
Cyangwa bijyanye cyane n'ibyo babakaye bafite
cyangwa bashobora kugira?

101
00:05:41,877 --> 00:05:45,187
niba ari ibikurikira bibiri,
hari uburyo mu bijyanye no kwamamaza,

102
00:05:45,187 --> 00:05:49,395
bushobora kongera ibyiyumvo byo gushaka

103
00:05:49,395 --> 00:05:51,840
ariko hari n'ibindi byinshi wakora aho.

104
00:05:52,292 --> 00:05:54,738
Ikindi gikurikira ni 
uko ibintu bigaragara ku isoko.

105
00:05:54,738 --> 00:05:59,097
uko ibintu bigaragara ku isoko ni urundi rwego rwo hejuru,
niba ushaka kubinyuza muri iyi nzira.

106
00:05:59,097 --> 00:06:00,808
Bitewe n'uko abakiriya babibona.

107
00:06:00,808 --> 00:06:04,209
By'ibanze ni urwego 
rw'abakiriya ufite,

108
00:06:04,209 --> 00:06:06,453
hanyuman n'ikibazo ni, isoko ringana rite?

109
00:06:06,453 --> 00:06:11,320
Ni abantu bangahe, amakampani angahe ashobora kuba muri iri soko?

110
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,494
Bashobora bihoraho kugura ibicuruzwa byanjye?

111
00:06:14,774 --> 00:06:17,314
kandi uko iminsi igenda, iki gice gituma ibikorwa bikura?

112
00:06:18,344 --> 00:06:20,686
Cyangwa ni igice gituma mpagama 
cyangwa gituma nsubira inyuma?

113
00:06:21,581 --> 00:06:25,193
Yego cyane, igice gituma ukura 
kiguhesha ubutaka bwera kurusha ubundi,

114
00:06:25,193 --> 00:06:27,637
ariko rero niba ufite
igitekerezo kimomeye cy'agaciro,

115
00:06:27,637 --> 00:06:33,286
ububabare bw'abakiriya  wakemura,

116
00:06:33,286 --> 00:06:36,624
n'igice kigusubiza inyuma cyaba ari neza,

117
00:06:36,624 --> 00:06:39,290
ariko igice gituma utera imbere nicyo kibyoroshya

118
00:06:39,290 --> 00:06:42,783
kuko ntabwo uba ugomba kurwana
n'abo muba muhanganye.

119
00:06:42,783 --> 00:06:45,050
ku migabane ku masoko iba igabanuka.

120
00:06:45,626 --> 00:06:47,355
Ikintu cya Gatatu
ushaka kurebaho

121
00:06:47,355 --> 00:06:49,216
Ni uko ibintu bigaragara mu bukungu.

122
00:06:49,216 --> 00:06:54,266
Ibi wakabitekerejeho
kugirango urebe ko ibikorwa byawe bizaramba.

123
00:06:54,772 --> 00:06:58,406
bisobanura ko urinda ibiciro
ukagerageza kumva

124
00:06:58,406 --> 00:07:01,557
niba wagera ku ntego zawe
z'ibiciro ku isoko

125
00:07:02,277 --> 00:07:03,910
kugirango ubashe ibyo biciro.

126
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:07,974
wabitekerejeho muri icyo gice, kugirango
ubashe kubona inyungu igihe kirekire

127
00:07:10,184 --> 00:07:12,164
aho bigeze ni aho wakavuze

128
00:07:12,185 --> 00:07:15,205
" Ni ubwoko bumwe bw'ubucuruzi,
mfite mu bikorwa byanjye,

129
00:07:15,205 --> 00:07:20,050
Mu ruhererekane rw'ibiciro
n'inyungu bijyana ku kuvuga,

130
00:07:20,050 --> 00:07:22,596
' Iki ni igikorwa kizaramba,
Ni igikorwa gishoboka.'"

131
00:07:22,596 --> 00:07:25,020
Niyo mpamvu uko ibintu bigaragara ku masoko
byagatekerejweho cyane

132
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,371
kandi mwakabaye mubisuzuma.

133
00:07:26,371 --> 00:07:28,434
ndabyumva ko ushobora kuba udafite amakuru ahagije

134
00:07:28,434 --> 00:07:30,238
mu bipimo byose mu ntangiriro,

135
00:07:30,238 --> 00:07:33,662
Ariko uru ni urugendo rwo Kwiga
nk'uko twamaze kubivuga mbere/

136
00:07:34,309 --> 00:07:38,216
ikindi gice ni umuvuduko 
wo kubyara inyungu?

137
00:07:39,066 --> 00:07:45,942
Urebye kubyara amafaranga,
ni amafaranga agenda aza muri Kanmpani.

138
00:07:45,942 --> 00:07:49,086
Uyu niwo mwuka muhumeka
muri Kampani,

139
00:07:49,086 --> 00:07:53,549
Ibi byerekana umuvuduko ufite mu kugera 
ku ntego zo kubona amafaranga.

140
00:07:53,549 --> 00:07:57,929
ni nako bizorohereza kampani 
kubaho igihe kirekire.

141
00:07:58,289 --> 00:08:01,531
Ikindi gice tugomba kujyaho impaka
 ni uko ukoresha amahirwe,

142
00:08:01,531 --> 00:08:05,419
Bigenda gake gake mu buryo ukoresha 
amahirwe uko iminsi igenda.

143
00:08:05,419 --> 00:08:08,889
Ikibazo aha ni
icyo ukeneye kwibaza,

144
00:08:08,889 --> 00:08:13,741
ese ushobora cyangwa ufite ubushobozi ukeneye kugira

145
00:08:13,741 --> 00:08:17,097
kugirango ubashe gukora ibicuruzwa byawe?
ndetse unabicuruze.

146
00:08:17,097 --> 00:08:19,832
Ikibazo kindi ni ukumenyana n'abantu.

147
00:08:20,372 --> 00:08:23,052
Ni ikintu ba rwiyemezamirimo bakabaye 
batekerezaho cyane.

148
00:08:23,052 --> 00:08:26,167
KUko uba ushingiye 
ku buryo uziranye n'abantu banyuranye

149
00:08:26,167 --> 00:08:28,130
Biba bigoye ko waba ufite byose mu ntangiriro,

150
00:08:28,130 --> 00:08:30,478
Uba ushingiye ku buryo uzwi n'abantu.

151
00:08:30,478 --> 00:08:32,857
Bishobora kuba kuba ubizi 
cyangwa kuba ufite amafaranga,

152
00:08:32,857 --> 00:08:36,965
Inkunga mu kuba wagera
ku bakiriya b'imena, n'abandi

153
00:08:36,965 --> 00:08:38,574
ariko ni ibyo gutekerezaho cyane.

154
00:08:38,574 --> 00:08:42,367
Ikibazo ni niba hari amwe muri
 ayo mahirwe uzabona

155
00:08:42,367 --> 00:08:46,458
Ushobora kuba ubufasha 
muri ubwo buryo abantu bakuzi.

156
00:08:46,458 --> 00:08:50,662
kandi amwe muri ayo mahirwe
ushobora kubonamo amahirwe make

157
00:08:50,662 --> 00:08:52,808
mu gihe ugerageza 
gukoresha ayo mahirwe.

158
00:08:52,908 --> 00:08:56,570
Byanyuma, mu byo wibaza,

159
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:59,686
Ni ayahe mahirwe
y'amahirwe muri iri soko?

160
00:09:00,576 --> 00:09:05,045
Ese abo muhanganye bashobora kugutsinda?

161
00:09:05,045 --> 00:09:10,522
kubera ibiciciro byo hasi
y'agaciro watekereza,

162
00:09:10,522 --> 00:09:12,400
Komereza aho?

163
00:09:14,155 --> 00:09:17,571
cyangwa wasanga hari amasoko
afite inyungu kurusha ayo yandi?

164
00:09:17,571 --> 00:09:23,179
aho uvuga, " Yego, iyi iri kumpesha 
amahoro mu mutwe.

165
00:09:23,179 --> 00:09:26,212
Nshobora gukomeza,
abakiriya banjye bakunda ibicuruzwa byanjye,

166
00:09:26,212 --> 00:09:30,121
ihiganwa ntabwo 
rikomeye cyane. Reka tubikore

167
00:09:31,229 --> 00:09:36,113
Bwanyuma, reka dukomeze tubyegere
turebe uko imikurire y'igikorwa imeze,

168
00:09:36,113 --> 00:09:39,357
Ushobora kwibaza,
Ese idirishya ry'amahirwe rirafunguye?

169
00:09:39,357 --> 00:09:42,055
Ese iri ni isoko nshobora kwinjira none aha?

170
00:09:42,055 --> 00:09:44,562
ndetse niba abakiriya biteguye
kugura ibicuruzwa byanjye?

171
00:09:44,562 --> 00:09:48,371
Cyangwa niba iri soko ari ryo nagafatiye
igihe cyo kuriteza imbere no kurizingura?

172
00:09:49,501 --> 00:09:53,808
Ibikorwa byawe byagufasha
kurema isoko

173
00:09:53,808 --> 00:09:56,801
ariko menya ko bifata igihe,

174
00:09:56,801 --> 00:10:01,073
kuko uba ushora imari
mu isoko rikura

175
00:10:01,073 --> 00:10:04,190
kandi abakiriya bashobora kuba
 badahari cyane

176
00:10:04,190 --> 00:10:08,588
kandi biteguye gutanga amafaranga yabo
bagura igicuruzwa byawe.

177
00:10:09,418 --> 00:10:11,670
Amahirwe araza kandi akagenda.

178
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:17,101
Gerageza gusuzuma ubu buryo bwo kubara igihe
mu gihe uri gushaka amahirwe.

179
00:10:17,101 --> 00:10:19,507
Ikindi wakabaye
ukeneye gutekerezaho 

180
00:10:19,507 --> 00:10:21,961
Ni niba amahirwe y'isoko
uri gushaka

181
00:10:21,961 --> 00:10:26,355
kandi riguha ubutaka
bizatuma utera indi ntambwe mu bindi bice bikurikira,

182
00:10:26,491 --> 00:10:28,375
aho ushobora gukora ibintu byinshi.

183
00:10:28,375 --> 00:10:31,302
None rero, ayo ni amahirwe y'isoko

184
00:10:31,302 --> 00:10:37,187
aguhesha imbere 
heza ho gucuruza?

185
00:10:37,886 --> 00:10:40,395
Tekereza amasoko agukurura cyane

186
00:10:40,395 --> 00:10:43,927
Yagufasha guha ishusho
umwirondoro w'umuryango wanyu.

187
00:10:43,927 --> 00:10:47,688
Mu buryo bwiza, abandi bantu
bazareba neza ibicuruzwa byawe,

188
00:10:47,688 --> 00:10:49,642
kandi uko abakiriya bareba neza ibicuruzwa byawe

189
00:10:49,642 --> 00:10:52,833
bishobora gutuma 
ugera no ku yandi masoko menshi

190
00:10:52,833 --> 00:10:57,330
Bwanyuma, ikibazo kivuka,
ushobora kwihagararaho igihe kirekire?

191
00:10:57,330 --> 00:11:01,951
Hari amwe mu masoko 
aho udushya tuza byihuse,


192
00:11:01,951 --> 00:11:04,228
ku buryo bisaba gushoramo menshi.

193
00:11:04,228 --> 00:11:08,107
mu kuvugurura ubushobozi bwawe,
no kongera ubwiza bw'ibicuruzwa byawe,

194
00:11:08,107 --> 00:11:11,844
Kub=girango ubashe 
kwihagararaho igihe kirekire.

195
00:11:11,844 --> 00:11:14,671
Kuko abo muhatana 
bashobora kugutsinda

196
00:11:14,671 --> 00:11:16,890
kandi bakaba banatanga ibicuruzwa byiza kurusha ibyawe

197
00:11:17,944 --> 00:11:20,027
Icyo kibao ni ikindi.

198
00:11:20,220 --> 00:11:23,119
Nk'uko ubibona, hari ibintu
 byinshi byo kwitabwaho,

199
00:11:23,119 --> 00:11:26,102
Gusuzuma isoko si akazi koroshye,

200
00:11:26,102 --> 00:11:29,384
cyane cyane iyo 
bimwe mu bipimo bidahamye

201
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,853
Bimwe mubyo 
ushobora kumenya,

202
00:11:32,529 --> 00:11:35,220
Aka nti gashobora 
kuba akazi k'abahanga

203
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:40,618
kuvuga ibi, " Aya ni amahirwe
ampa amahitamo meza."

204
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:46,814
Ari kuguha 
imyumvire ifatika 

205
00:11:46,814 --> 00:11:49,014
Ariko ibirenze ku imyumvire,

206
00:11:49,014 --> 00:11:51,893
Ni ukumva
 bijyanye n'ubwenge 

207
00:11:52,786 --> 00:11:56,131
Hagati y'imyumvire no gusobanukirwa,

208
00:11:56,131 --> 00:11:58,991
Ni irihe soko ushaka kwibandaho,

209
00:11:58,991 --> 00:12:02,657
Aha ni ahantu hagati
wagafashe,


210
00:12:02,657 --> 00:12:04,910
Kandi niho ngusabye kijya.

211
00:12:05,229 --> 00:12:06,731
Gerageza kubona amakuru,

212
00:12:06,731 --> 00:12:09,941
Gira igitekerezo gifite amakuru,
menshi ahagije bishoboka

213
00:12:09,941 --> 00:12:11,764
Mbere yo kujya guhura n'isoko,

214
00:12:11,764 --> 00:12:13,646
Kuko wibuka
ibyo twavuze mu ntangiriro,

215
00:12:13,646 --> 00:12:15,272
Ni ukureba mbere yo kubiba!

216
00:12:15,272 --> 00:12:17,015
Twanzura, iki ni igitekerezo nyacyo

217
00:12:17,015 --> 00:12:19,460
" mfite amahirwe menshi y'amasoko

218
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:21,492
Nshobora gukoresha."

219
00:12:21,492 --> 00:12:25,530
Urabona hano,
Ugasuzuma ayo mahirwe.

220
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:27,205
Ugahitamo ubutaka bwera kurusha ibindi bwose

221
00:12:27,205 --> 00:12:30,773
Aho uvuga, " Aha niho nishimiye kuba,

222
00:12:30,773 --> 00:12:34,240
Aha niho nkunda
ubwoko bw'umuryango nakoze."

223
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:38,025
Ukinjira mu gic hanyuma, uko iminsi igenda,
niba iki gikora ushobora kugira

224
00:12:38,025 --> 00:12:41,342
uburyo bunyuranye bwo kwinjira no
mu bindi.

225
00:12:41,342 --> 00:12:44,313
Ubu ni  ubuzima nka rwiyemezamirimo

226
00:12:44,313 --> 00:12:47,052
Kandi uru rugendo nti rurangira
kandi nti rwakarangiranye

227
00:12:47,052 --> 00:12:49,258
n'isoko rya mbere wajyamo.

228
00:12:49,548 --> 00:12:53,341
Ahubwo, wakabibonye nko
kubaka ubufatanye bukomeye

229
00:12:53,341 --> 00:12:56,573
Rigerageza guhaza ibice binyuranye.

230
00:12:56,573 --> 00:12:58,118
Murakoze cyane.

231
00:12:58,118 --> 00:13:00,526
Ntegereje kubabona
mu bindi bice.
